-- China Mutual Funds Lose $52 Billion in Second Quarter, Securities Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-20T23:13:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-20/china-mutual-funds-lose-52-billion-in-second-quarter-securities-reports.html

          
          
             Chinese mutual funds had a combined
loss of 351.3 billion yuan ($52 billion) in the second quarter,
China Securities Journal reported today, citing TX Investment
Consulting Co.  
 Sixty fund-management companies cut their portfolio equity
holdings for 652 funds to 73.25 percent in the second quarter
from 81.95 percent at the end of the first quarter, according to
the Beijing-based newspaper.  
